  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to evaluate the prevalence of sustained ventricular and
      supraventricular rhythm disorders in patients implanted with a CONTAK RENEWAL TR2 ventricular
      resynchronization therapy (CRT) device
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
